{{Han compound|甡|又|t1=broom|t2=hand|ls=ic}} – to hold a broom which is made of bamboo.

===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|alt=篲,𥱵,𥶙}}

{{zh-ref|Sagart (2021)}} modifies {{zh-ref|Baxter and Sagart's (2014)}} reconstruction to {{m|und|*sə-m-pʰˤut-s}}, deriving it from a root {{m|und|*pʰˤut||dust}}, with the iambic form of the prefix {{m|und|*s-}}, which derives circumstantial nouns, and the prefix {{m|und|*m-}}, which derives verbs of volitional action from nouns, and relates it to {{och-l|勃}} and {{och-l|孛}}.

